Setup instructions for custom check-netapp pnp4nagios templates
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

These instructions help you in installing the customized pnp4nagios templates in your nagios environment.
The templates are built up in this manner:

<command_name>.php

NP4Nagios will automatically select the template with same name as the check plugin command_name.

Step by step instructions:

1. Check your version of pnp4nagios. Please use 0.6.x, http://www.pnp4nagios.org/.
2. Copy all templates (check-netapp-PerfCpu.php, etc.) to the existing pnp4nagios directory "templates", at mostly /usr/local/pnp4nagios/share/htdocs/templates . Please check your configuration paths for pnp4nagios.
3. set the permissions on the templates to 644, for example "chmod 644 check-netapp-*.php".
4. Please adapt the given "netapp.cfg" for command configurations.
5. Restart nagios processes and check the graphs.



